query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(mc cn) NoMergeJoin(cn mc t mk) NoMergeJoin(cn mc mk t k) */ select min(t.title) AS movie_title
from movie_companies AS mc
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[de]'
inner join title AS t
on mc.movie_id = t.id
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'character-name-in-title';
